Package com.flipkart.client

Class FlipFitAdminClientMenu

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.client.FlipFitAdminClientMenu
public class FlipFitAdminClientMenu extends Object
Client-side menu for FlipFit Admin operations. This class handles user interactions for managing gym centres and gym owners, including viewing, approving, rejecting, and removing records.
